Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坏消息  换成纽约地产的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bad news: in New York real estate time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是至少一个月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that's a month minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但谢谢你让我暂住在这  哈娜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But thanks for letting me crash here, Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不客气  你的其他东西呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No worries. Where's all your stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在这\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有洗衣机和烘干机吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You have a washer and dryer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把脏衣服拿来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You brought your laundry?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.44,0:03:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  还带了这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. And I brought this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走一个庆祝下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Celebratory shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.48,0:03:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下班后吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe after work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:03:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泽蒂  这是克罗斯比  我们的新室友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Zadie, meet Crosby, our new roommate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:03:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我错过家庭会议了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did I miss a house meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应该一起商量这种事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're supposed to discuss these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是暂时的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's only temporary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的公寓水管漏了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have a plumbing issue in my apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碰我的果汁架\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't touch my juice shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早六点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}6:00 A.M. this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工头到达宾夕法尼亚州萨默塞特的欣欣草农场后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}foreman arrives at Rushing Meadow Farm in Somerset, Pennsylvania,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现农场主的房门被闯入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and finds the front door of the owner's house broken into.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他进去后发现了这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He goes inside to find this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受害者是杰克·卡特莱特  事业小成的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Victims are Jack Cartwright, very successful
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,农场所有者  还有他十七岁的儿子埃里克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}proprietor of the farm, and his 17-year-old son, Eric.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桌子被人翻遍了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That desk has been ransacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是有人在找钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Could be someone was looking for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了拿到钱把他俩都杀了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And murdered them both to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克是杰克前妻的儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Eric is Jack's son from his first marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八年前  杰克二婚娶了艾米莉亚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Eight years ago, Jack then remarried Amelia,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新罕布什尔州的一位老师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a schoolteacher from New Hampshire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她领养了埃里克  然后他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She adopted Eric, and then they had
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了一个六岁的女儿格蕾茜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a six-year-old daughter named Gracie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈和女儿都失踪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Both the mom and the daughter are missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以入室抢劫变成了谋杀案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So it's a home invasion turned double murder
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又变成了绑架案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}turned double kidnapping?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.78,0:04:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:04:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要找的是这个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And this is who we're looking for:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}联调局通缉犯\N萨缪·拉特利奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨缪·拉特利奇  38岁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Samuel Rutledge, 38 years old,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近刚假释  之前坐了九年牢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}recently paroled after serving nine years
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因严重伤害罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}on an aggravated assault charge
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被关在康科德的州男子监狱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}at the State Prison for Men in Concord.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨默塞特警局发现他的脚环被劈成了两半\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Somerset PD found his ankle bracelet with the strap cut in two
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扔在了离卡特莱特家五英里的车道上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}five miles from the Cartwrights' driveway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后一小时前  一家纳舒厄的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then about an hour ago, surveillance cam
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油站监控拍到了这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}at a gas station in Nashua caught this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐在副驾驶的是萨姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's Sam in the passenger seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的搭档是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who's his partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是货车车主\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's the owner of that van,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个正在假释的罪犯  彼得·提蒙斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}another ex-con on parole named Peter Timmons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}彼得·提蒙斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在曼彻斯特的格林斯博罗监狱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He did five years at Greensboro Correctional
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因毒品罪坐了五年牢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in Manchester on a drug charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  他们不是同一个监狱的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wait, they weren't in prison together?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只知道  他们都在新罕布什尔州\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All we know is, they were in New Hampshire,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们开了492英里  跨越五个州犯下了这些罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they drove 492 miles through five states to commit these crimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正在回去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and now they're on their way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么袭击这家人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So why target this family?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么杀了两人  绑架妈妈和女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why kill the two men, take the mom and daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许他们没拿到想要的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe they didn't get what they wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉亚和格蕾茜可能是连带伤害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amelia and Gracie could be collateral.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们也可能是人体盾牌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They could also be human shields.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安珀紧急通告发出了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amber alert go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发了  还有针对小货车的协查通告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, and a BOLO on the van.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:05:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到两人之间的联系了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, I found their connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.68,0:06:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚环上的监控器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The monitor on that ankle bracelet
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追溯到一名叫巴里·桑兹的假释官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}traces to a parole officer named Barry Sands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}巴里·桑兹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据新罕布什尔州狱政局回复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}According to the New Hampshire DOC,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们两个都在被他监管\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he was supervising the both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  桑兹的位置在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Excellent. Where is Sands' location?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}康科德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康科德  与彼得最后的已知位置相同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Concord, same as Peter's last known.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨姆的情况我没有看到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not seeing anything for Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们分头行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, let's split it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴恩斯和我去找假释官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Barnes and I will talk to the parole officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克罗斯比  你去彼得的住处查查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Crosby, check out Peter's apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈娜  追踪鉴证的反馈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hana, follow up with Forensics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确保他们勘验现场时收集了触碰DNA\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Make sure they're processing the scene for touch DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉亚和格蕾茜也就是一时对他们有用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amelia and Gracie are only useful to these two until they're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}联邦调查局通缉令  萨缪·拉特利奇\N联邦调查局通缉令  彼得·提蒙斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦她们失去了用处  两个人就都会死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Soon as that happens, they're both dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毁坏卫星定位监控器在本州是重罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tampering with a GPS monitor is a felony in this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨姆面临再被关上三年的刑罚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sam's looking at another three years in lockup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}新罕布什尔州  康科德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对现在的他来说还算轻的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I'm guessing that's the least of his worries,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟还有凶杀和双人绑架呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}given the murders and the double abduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定彼得和他一起干的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You sure Peter was with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真不知道他们俩是哥们儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Didn't know they were pals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们俩每周和你的会面时间是一样的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Were their appointments at the same time each week?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  每周二\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, every Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨姆4点  彼得4点半\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sam at 4:00, Peter at 4:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃犯在你的等待室会面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Our fugitives met in your waiting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨姆是我们所谓的NH\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sam is what we call an NH,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:06:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"没有人性"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Not human."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果系统把你标记为魔鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If the system writes you off as a monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么还费劲去扮演其他角色呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}why bother acting like anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And Peter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从来都不暴力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Never violent,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他老婆给狱中的他送达离婚文件时他都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}not even when his wife served him divorce papers in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有个前妻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He has an ex-wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琳达·卡罗尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Linda Carroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和一个搞房地产的有钱人再婚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Remarried some wealthy real estate guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但彼得在狱里信了教\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But Peter found religion in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他宽恕了她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He forgave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能重新建立个家庭  洗心革面开始新生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wanted to start a new family, a new life on the up-and-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果彼得希望能重新来过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So if Peter wanted a second chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么他要把一切都搭上去帮助萨姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}why would he risk everything to help Sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱  性  钱  或者是作伴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Love, sex, money, or sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有萨姆的住址\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We don't have an address for Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他才出来6周\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's only been out six weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在393号公路上的布拉沃汽车旅馆住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Been staying at the Bravo Motel off of 393.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的客户都喜欢住在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Popular place for my clientele.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}新鲜出炉的披萨\N按您的要求定制
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚和这的经理谈过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just spoke to the manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨姆周一付了一周的房钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sam paid for a week in the room on Monday,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她之后就没见过他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and she hasn't seen him since.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫生间有洗漱用品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's toiletries in the bathroom
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣柜里挂着衬衣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and shirts hanging in the closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的推测是  他计划着要回来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My guess is, he's planning on coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.36,0:07:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do we got here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名牌手袋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Designer bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主方切割的3克拉钻戒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Three-carat princess cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚上穿的是大概800块的意大利皮鞋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}About 800 bucks of Italian leather on her feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这女人绝对不吝惜钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This woman is not hurting for cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些不是抓拍的照片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}These aren't candid photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是个有钱的妇女和她的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Another rich lady and her kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把照片发给哈娜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Send them to Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她运行人脸识别\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have her run face recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我联系一下克罗斯比\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm gonna check in with Crosby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在彼得的住处有什么发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What'd you find at Peter's apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边没有迹象显示他认识受害人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing here says this guy knew the victims
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者为什么他把他们作为目标\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or why he was targeting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那边有什么发现吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You got anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在萨姆旅馆的房间找到了一些照片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, we found some photos in Sam's motel room,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是监视照片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}surveillance pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.77,0:08:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管这个女的是什么人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Whoever this woman is,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们绝对是在跟踪她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they're definitely stalking her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对是同一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's definitely the same woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着是这样  她是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sure looks like it. Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琳达·卡罗尔  彼得的前妻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Linda Carroll, Peter's ex-wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他们要回康科德来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's why they're coming back to Concord.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是他们的下一个目标\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She's their next target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shh. It's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你转账了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You make the transfer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转了  不过要两个小时才能过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, but it's gonna take a couple of hours to go through.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不能接受  -求求你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Not acceptable! - Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从没说过要花两个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You never said it would take two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨姆  不过是耽搁了一点时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, Sam, it's just a minor delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, listen, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们按计划去袭击琳达家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We hit Linda's place like we planned,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事回头再处理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}take care of this after.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多钱呢  值得等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a lot of money. It's worth the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上车里去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get in the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要把我们带到哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where are you taking us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上你的臭嘴  上车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just shut your damn mouth and get in the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪儿偷的车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where'd you steal the truck?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓的  快点吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Doesn't matter. Just hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是搞错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There must be some mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}新罕布什尔州  彭布鲁克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得从不暴力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Peter's never been violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人在监狱会变的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, people do change in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说他杀害了一个十来岁的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So you're saying that he murdered a teenage boy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有他的父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and his father too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们的重点是要找到他绑架的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right now, our priority is to find the woman
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:10:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人和孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and the child that he abducted
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:11:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以免一切都太晚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}before it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有注意到最近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you aware that anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.19,0:11:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是在跟踪你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}might've been following you recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没注意  怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们认为你和你的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, we think that you and your family
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是彼得和萨姆的下一个目标\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}might be Peter and Sam's next target.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会在你家外面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll post officers outside your house
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派警官来保护你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to protect you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得出狱以后你见过他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you seen Peter since he got out of prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  但我们离婚以后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, but we kept in regular correspondence
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直有通信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}after our divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的假释官说他宽恕了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, his parole officer said he forgave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.79,0:11:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他希望我能往前走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He wanted me to move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们婚礼那天  他给我和我丈夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He wrote me and my husband
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.61,0:11:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寄了一首写得很有感情的诗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a lovely poem on our wedding day
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利出生时还给他写了一首\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and one for Henry at his birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不介意  我想看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you don't mind, I'd like to see those.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.93,0:12:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是什么事  你都可以告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, whatever it is, you can tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在彼得的假释听证会上做过证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I testified at Peter's parole hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉假释委员会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I told the parole board
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.54,0:12:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得绝对不会伤害任何人  而如今\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that Peter would never hurt anyone, and--and now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这不是你的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No. This isn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是那两个暴徒的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is the fault of two violent men,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中一个曾让你相信他们已经改过自新了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}one that convinced you they'd been reformed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到他人的好的一面并没有错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not a bad thing to see the good in people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人把这个社区称为"美国梦"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Some people call this neighborhood the American Dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫它"美国谎言"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I call it the American Lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:13:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要上厕所\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have to go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憋着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我真的必须要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I really have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了  亲爱的  会没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shh, honey. It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜欢带着累赘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't like having baggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.21,0:13:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就按计划行事  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We just stick to the plan, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就快成功了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-趴下  -为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Get on the floor. - What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做就是了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, Pete,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我们所说的二振\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}this here is what we call strike two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白  他们怎么会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't understand. How did they--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往后退  然后调头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just back up and turn around
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他们看到我们前  慢慢转过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}nice and slow before they see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开始觉得你和她们一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm beginning to think you're just like them:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.83,0:14:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个累赘  而远非有用的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}more of a liability than you are an asset.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我会怎样处理累赘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you know what I do with liabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没人给我们打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nobody called us about any ransom
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}新罕布什尔州  拉科尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索要艾米莉亚和格蕾茜的赎金  如果他们打了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}for Amelia or Gracie, and if they did--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会想办法付钱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we'd have found a way to pay it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰克或艾米莉亚提到过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did Jack or Amelia mention seeing anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.62,0:14:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在过去几天看到了什么奇怪的人或事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or anything out of the ordinary these last few days?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不怎么跟你们的女儿说话吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You don't talk to your daughter much?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉亚是个很难相处的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amelia was a challenging child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾称她为我的小豪猪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I used to call her my little porcupine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-她是个很漂亮的姑娘  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- She was a beautiful girl. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们经常对她这样说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}People were constantly telling her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在某个年纪  男孩子们蜂拥而来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then at a certain age, the boys came swarming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果艾米莉亚没那么醉心于她的书本的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amelia could've had them wrapped around her finger
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她本可以把他们玩弄于股掌之间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if she wasn't so wrapped up in her books.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是个聪明的姑娘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She's a smart girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她六岁时就跟我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She was only six years old, and she said to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"妈妈  我完全有能力为自己做饭"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Mommy, I'm perfectly capable of making my own dinner."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就让她做了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So I let her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-一年级学生自给自足\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Self-sufficient for a first grader.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酗酒者子女的共同特征\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But a common trait in the children of alcoholics.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你戒酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How long has it been
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多长时间了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}since you put down the bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我记不清有多少次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I-I can't count how many times
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醉醺醺地开车送我女儿去上学\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I drove my daughter to school drunk
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者扭得她肩膀脱臼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or dislocated her shoulder
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.03,0:15:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或扭伤她的胳膊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or twisted her arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不以此为荣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not proud of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当时病了  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You were sick, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在她十六岁那天的夏天  艾米莉亚让我戒酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amelia asked me to quit drinking the summer she turned 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说如果我爱她  我会戒的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Said if I loved her, I'd do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我戒不了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I couldn't do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕是为了我的小女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}even for my own little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正那个夏天没戒成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not that summer, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们当时在佛蒙特州的伊甸湖畔租了幢房子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We had rented a house on Lake Eden in Vermont.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就发生了意外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And then there was the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.17,0:16:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉亚的朋友  柯林斯家的儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amelia's friend, the Collins boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在桥上胡闹时摔了下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he was horsing around on a bridge, took a bad fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她看到了整件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She saw the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那以后艾米莉亚就不一样了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amelia was never the same after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她得了抑郁症\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She suffered from depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至在她嫁给杰克  并收养埃里克后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Even after she married Jack and adopted Eric,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.46,0:16:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也从未有过好转\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}never got any better...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到他们有了格蕾茜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}until they had Gracie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做母亲改变了她吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Motherhood changed her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉亚成为了欢乐的化身\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amelia became joy personified.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.67,0:16:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她告诉我  "妈妈  我有了第二次机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She said to me, "Mama, I've got a second chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉自己好像重生了"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I feel like I've been reborn."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但后来艾米莉亚就变得艾米莉亚...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But then Amelia being Amelia...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.52,0:16:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.25,0:16:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾茜出生后他们搬到了宾夕法尼亚州\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They moved to Pennsylvania after Gracie was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经五年没见过她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We haven't seen her for five years--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者我们的外孙女了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or our granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他名叫大卫·柯林斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}His name is David Collins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}明星运动员在伊甸湖的事故中受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他从一座桥上跳水  入水姿势不对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He dived off a bridge, hit the water wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双侧肩膀都摔骨折了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}broke both his shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定很糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It must've been awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而艾米莉亚目睹了整个过程吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And Amelia saw the whole thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  这件事再加上她那酗酒的父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, that, coupled with her alcoholic father,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:16:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她的情况急剧恶化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}sent her into a spiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:17:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她好多年都不跟她的家人说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She hasn't spoken to her family for years,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至在她嫁人  格蕾茜出生以后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}even after she got married and Gracie was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个外孙女是个重归于好的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, the granddaughter was a chance at reconciliation,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而她依然选择远离她的父母\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}yet she still chose to stay away from her parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为这事与他们有关吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You think they're involved somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们似乎不会做这样的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They don't seem right for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这案子不能按照常理推断\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing is right about this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得·提蒙斯是位非暴力的和平主义者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Peter Timmons is a nonviolent pacifist
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他杀了两个人  然后盯上了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who murdered two people, then targeted his ex-wife
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友好离婚的前妻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}after an amicable divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这与艾米莉亚没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's no connection to Amelia,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想唯一的动机是  钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so the only motive I can think of is...money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚接到匡提科市DNA检测部门的电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just got off the phone with the DNA unit at Quantico.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们对艾米莉亚死去的丈夫和房间内发现的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They ran touch DNA on Amelia's dead husband
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾茜的小毯子做了接触性DNA检验\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and Gracie's blankie they found at the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.71,0:17:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果并不匹配\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以杰克不是生物学上的父亲吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So Jack isn't the biological father?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.32,0:17:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不是  -那是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- No. - Then who is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我上传格蕾茜的DNA数据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If I upload Gracie's DNA profile,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以从DNA联合索引系统开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we can start with CODIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管希望不大  但这是个开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, it's a long shot, but it's a start.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}彼得·提蒙斯  逮捕记录\N巴里·桑兹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到匹配的人了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You get a match?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:17:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:18:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就在系统里  因为我们认识他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's in the system because we know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾茜的父亲是彼得·提蒙斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gracie's father is Peter Timmons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}DNA联合索引系统-819422  彼得·提蒙斯\N格蕾茜·卡特莱特的DNA数据与在格林斯博罗服刑的\N囚犯彼得·提蒙斯相吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根本不是绑架\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This isn't a kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一家人在逃亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is a family on the run.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得·提蒙斯是我这里唯一一位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Peter Timmons was one of my only inmates
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}新罕布什尔州  曼彻斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不参与身体或语言冲突的囚犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}not to engage in physical or verbal conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这里大多是很暴力的罪犯吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You have mostly violent criminals here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.71,0:18:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕是毒品罪犯  那些像彼得的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Even the drug offenders, ones like Peter,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通常也会为了生存不得不变得很暴力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}usually have to turn violent to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他从不参加吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But he stayed above the fray?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只关注他的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Focused on his future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想看看彼得在这里时的来访记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'd like to see a log of Peter's visitors during his time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么特别关注的人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Anyone in particular?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉亚·卡特莱特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amelia Cartwright?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识她吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  艾米莉亚不是个访客\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, Amelia wasn't a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我们创意写作课的老师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She was our creative writing teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.09,0:18:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得在她那儿上课\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and Peter was in her class--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一周两次上了三年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}twice a week for three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们待在一起的时间很长啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's a lot of time to spend together
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在没有监管的情况下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}without supervision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得没有暴力倾向\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, well, Peter wasn't violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他想做个情人而非斗士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And if he wanted to be a lover and not a fighter,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:18:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全可以理解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:19:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里的时候和艾米莉亚生了孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He fathered Amelia's child during his time here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是他们潜逃时带走的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the same child they took on the run
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.59,0:19:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在暴力犯罪之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with a violent criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为他喜欢诗歌呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just thought he liked poetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得在艾米莉亚课上的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Was there a specific computer that Peter used
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有用过一台特定的电脑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when he was in Amelia's writing class?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有  在实验室里  走这边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, in the lab. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.51,0:19:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪一台是彼得用的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Which one did Peter use?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直用最后一排的第二台\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Second one in the back, always.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说  各位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Listen up, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下你手头的工作  回避一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Save your work, and let's clear out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我祖母在1986年的时候也有这台电脑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My grandmother had this computer in, like, 1986.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  监狱长给的彼得在监狱里用的邮箱和密码\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here, the warden gave us peter's prison email and password.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.29,0:19:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给当地报纸专栏的啰嗦稿件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Long-winded op-eds to local papers,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}总编  罪犯也是人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给他前妻的辞藻华丽的信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}flowery messages to his ex-wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾觉得我们的结合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"I once thought you and I were joined
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}琳达·卡罗尔  生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像一棵老橡树的根部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Like the roots of an ancient oak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我们拥有的都已逝去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know what we had was fleeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们本是一根树枝上的两片树叶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We were two leaves on a single branch."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟琳达·卡罗尔给我们的信上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's the same poetic tone
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗歌的语气一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}as the letters Linda Carroll gave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但没有和艾米丽亚往来的邮件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But nothing to or from Amelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}未找到发给或来自艾米莉亚·卡特莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非它们从没被发出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Unless they were never sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个恐怖分子大概在2010年停用的把戏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a trick terrorists abandoned circa 2010.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在草稿箱写一封邮件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You write an email in the drafts folder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给某人你的用户名让他登录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You give someone your username and log-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登录之后阅读并回复  但是邮件从未被发出过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They log in, read and respond, but the email never gets sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样狱警就没法监控他们的联络\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And prison staff can't monitor their correspondence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得  艾米莉亚  彼得  艾米莉亚  这持续了多久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Peter, Amelia. Amelia, Peter. How long's this going for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.42,0:20:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.06,0:20:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-萨姆  -你要干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Sam. - What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-嗨  -妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Hey. - Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你要带我去哪  -不要啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Where are you taking me? - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨姆  等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sam, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们要带妈妈去哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where are they taking Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把钱转账了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you make the transfer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在努力  我在努力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm trying. I'm trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在尝试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's trying now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  格蕾茜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's okay, Gracie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你妈妈出任何事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I won't let anything happen to your mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:20:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.21,0:21:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在  还在  还在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's--it's--it's--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.73,0:21:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了  求你了  求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please, please, please, please, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-萨姆  -不要  不要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Sam! - Please don't. Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.96,0:21:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾茜  呆在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gracie, stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-求你了  求你了  -等等  等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Please, please don't. - Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-求你  -喂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Please. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别管\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stay out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.26,0:21:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说已经转账了  但是钱没有转过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She said she made the transfer, but it didn't go through.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.51,0:21:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转账还没有被处理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, it says it's still pending.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  那是很多钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look, it is a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.39,0:21:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转账是需要时间的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It takes time for it to go through.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这你早就知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Which you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在太晚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's too late now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.35,0:21:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早本还可以解决\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}First thing this morning would've worked,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.94,0:21:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在你是个失踪人口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but now you're a missing person
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个新英格兰都有找你的大头照\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with your face plastered all over New England.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.27,0:21:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你走进一家银行会把我们俩都送进了监狱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You walk into that bank, it puts us both into jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.94,0:21:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能杀了她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can't just shoot her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.11,0:21:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的孩子还在看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Her kid's watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.28,0:21:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个就轮到她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And she'll be next.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.07,0:21:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨姆  不能这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sam, this is a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和这些女人有什么关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What is it with you and these ladies, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.45,0:21:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟她这样的贱人有一腿吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You got a thing for bitches like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者你是个恋童癖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Or is it kids that are your thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.46,0:21:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边有个小女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's a little girl in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯洁的  未被触碰过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She's pure, untouched,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.55,0:21:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和她妈妈一样好看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}nice looks like her mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.22,0:21:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能解决这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.93,0:22:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不一定非要是我去银行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't have to be the one to go into the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.77,0:22:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的父亲会去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My father will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.35,0:22:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.77,0:22:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他住在康科德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He lives in Concord.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.11,0:22:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我带到他家里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take me to his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.11,0:22:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把钱转给他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll transfer him the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.48,0:22:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他会去银行把钱取出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and he'll go in and pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.11,0:22:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后一道把警察引过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And bring the cops back with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.32,0:22:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不会的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, he won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.86,0:22:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我叫他不要这么做他就不会的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He won't, not if I tell him not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.62,0:22:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了  求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.70,0:22:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这笔钱足够给你任何你想要的新开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It is enough for any new beginning you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.70,0:22:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把它们全部给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I will give you every penny
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.58,0:22:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你能放过我和我女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if you just let me and my daughter go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.42,0:22:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.17,0:22:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我求求你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please, I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.26,0:22:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得给艾米莉亚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}From Peter to Amelia:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.63,0:22:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我见到你之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Before I met you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.68,0:22:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能与他人共享灵魂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I could not fathom sharing my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.18,0:22:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今我必须如此  你我之灵魂相生相伴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now I know I must, for your soul is its mate,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.64,0:22:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终将合一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and they must become one."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.39,0:22:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望她会给这首诗打不及格\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I hope she gave him a D on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.27,0:22:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉亚给彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}From Amelia back to Peter:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撑我度过这周的唯一动力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"The only thing that gets me through the week
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.98,0:22:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是知道我将见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is knowing I'll see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.36,0:22:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的所有  我爱你"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You are my everything. I love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.94,0:22:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来很真诚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That actually sounds sincere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.61,0:22:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很真诚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It is sincere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:22:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉亚脆弱而压抑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amelia was vulnerable and depressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.15,0:23:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得是在趁虚而入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and Peter was taking advantage.
