Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.91,0:25:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟着她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Go with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.03,0:25:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是他们试图报警  你知道该怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They try to call the cops, you know what to do.
