Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.52,0:25:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是他们家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This isn't their house.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.98,0:25:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们来这干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then what are we doing here?
