Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.62,0:28:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受害者身上没钱包也没身份证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No wallet or ID on the victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.33,0:28:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我猜你们认识他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I'm guessing you know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.50,0:28:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们的另一个逃犯  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your other fugitive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.92,0:28:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  萨姆·拉特利奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, Sam Rutledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.00,0:28:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用斧子剖开腹部然后在胸部补了一枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gutted with an ax and then shot in the chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.96,0:28:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们低估彼得了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I guess we underestimated Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.89,0:29:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目击者说他们看到女人和小孩了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did the witness say they saw a woman and a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.39,0:29:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的失踪人口吗  我还没问到那\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your missing persons? I hadn't gotten there yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.06,0:29:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们来时我还在问她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was still interviewing her when you rolled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.56,0:29:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去问她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll go talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.49,0:29:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈娜  什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hana, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.36,0:29:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们顺着那些GPS坐标\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We followed those GPS coordinates
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.07,0:29:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了他们藏东西的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to the nest egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.20,0:29:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个旅行箱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's some kind of steamer trunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.57,0:29:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到这里时已经被挖出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was already dug up when we got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.66,0:29:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-里面有东西吗  -是空的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Anything in it? - Empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.91,0:29:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这里到处都是轮胎印\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But there's tire tracks everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.58,0:29:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克罗斯比在检查比对  有人比我们先到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Crosby's off checking them out. Somebody beat us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.42,0:29:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jess?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.09,0:29:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是彼得和艾米莉亚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Probably Peter and Amelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.34,0:29:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们杀了萨姆  丢下车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They killed Sam, ditched the van,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.97,0:29:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开了辆失窃的福特皮卡跑了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and took off in a stolen Ford pickup.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.68,0:29:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定还没跑远\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can't have gotten far.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.97,0:29:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们该叫鉴识科的人过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We should get ERT down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.97,0:29:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们看看这些轮胎印是不是那辆福特的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They can see if these tracks match that Ford.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.27,0:29:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也能检查一下这个箱子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They can also test this trunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.06,0:29:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埋得很深  但上面也可能有DNA\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was buried pretty deep, but it's probably full of DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.69,0:29:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  让他们查查看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay. Run it and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.95,0:30:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鉴识科说检查完旅行箱了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tech said he's done with the steamer trunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.78,0:30:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他把报告发过来了吗  -发了  收到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Did he send the report? - Yep. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.00,0:30:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"残存痕迹与美国货币一致"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Trace elements consistent with U.S. currency."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.83,0:30:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以之前里面确实有钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So there was cash in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.17,0:30:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁先拿到的  彼得还是艾米莉亚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who got to it first, Peter or Amelia?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.34,0:30:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.50,0:30:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面的DNA是大卫·柯林斯的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}DNA found belongs to David Collins.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.88,0:30:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}样本  大卫·柯林斯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.80,0:30:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉亚的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amelia's friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.88,0:30:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桥上事故那个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the one from the accident on the bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.97,0:30:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪  他有案底吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's weird. Does he have a record?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.80,0:30:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在一所私立学校当教练\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's a coach at a private school
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.85,0:30:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}麦卡锡  工作经历  高中  大卫  柯林斯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.18,0:30:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要DNA和指纹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that requires DNA and prints.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.06,0:30:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉亚为什么要把她和彼得共有的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why would Amelia give him the coordinates
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.85,0:30:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存款的位置告诉他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to the nest egg she shared with Peter?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.73,0:30:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她自己随时都可以拿到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She could have gotten it anytime by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.98,0:30:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能递给我一下彼得给他前妻的信吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can you pass me the letters that Peter sent to his ex-wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.11,0:30:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.15,0:30:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}大卫·柯林斯  艾米莉亚·卡特赖特  萨姆·拉特利奇
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.16,0:30:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我这儿的日子充满着嘈杂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"My days here are filled with noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.07,0:30:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁窗哐当作响  脏水冲洗食盘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Bars clanging. Slop hitting trays.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.87,0:30:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拳头落在身上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Men's fists on flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.58,0:30:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我充耳不闻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"But all I hear is the deafening silence
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.41,0:30:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯沉浸在让你失望的寂寂无声中"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"of having disappointed you."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.33,0:30:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这跟他写给艾米莉亚的狱中诗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's a far cry from the prison poetry
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.96,0:30:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he sent Amelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.59,0:31:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是彼得写的  艾米莉亚写的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Peter didn't write these. Amelia did.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.72,0:31:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她故意设计他的前妻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She was setting up the ex-wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.55,0:31:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她以为彼得原谅她了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}making her think Peter had forgiven her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.14,0:31:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她放松警惕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That way, she's an easier target.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.85,0:31:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说不是彼得主导的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're saying Peter's not leading this?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.14,0:31:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可能杀了萨姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He might've killed Sam,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.85,0:31:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是艾米莉亚在发号施令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but Amelia's calling the shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.06,0:31:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和钱无关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This was never about the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.40,0:31:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是艾米莉亚需要控制她生命中的男人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is about Amelia's need to control the men in her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.11,0:31:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有大卫的地址吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We have an address for David?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.48,0:31:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在蒂尔顿  屋主是玛丽·柯林斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Residence in Tilton owned by Mary Collins.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.57,0:31:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来他和姐姐住在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Looks like he lives with his sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.62,0:31:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}新罕布什尔州  蒂尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.78,0:31:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽·柯林斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mary Collins?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.87,0:31:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是联调局的拉克鲁瓦探员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm Agent LaCroix of the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.25,0:31:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们找到我弟弟了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you find my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.66,0:31:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大卫  我们以为他住这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}David? We thought he lived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.08,0:31:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是啊  但他不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He does, but he's disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.79,0:31:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他早上去上班\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He went to work this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.92,0:31:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但学校说他没出现过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but the school said he never showed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.84,0:31:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给他打了一个小时的电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've been calling his cell for an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.63,0:31:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他没接\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and he's not answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.55,0:31:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.01,0:31:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在找一个女人  她被绑架了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're looking for a woman who's been abducted.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.80,0:31:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们觉得你弟弟也许卷入其中了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We think your brother might be involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.64,0:31:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉亚·卡特赖特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amelia Cartwright?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.39,0:31:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个艾米莉亚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That Amelia?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.64,0:31:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.73,0:31:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大卫绝不会伤害她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}David would never hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.02,0:31:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他爱了她一辈子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's been in love with her his whole life,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.98,0:32:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕她那样对他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}even after what she did to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.73,0:32:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桥上意外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The accident on the bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.19,0:32:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是意外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was no accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.69,0:32:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在伊甸湖边的房屋消暑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We were at our house out on Lake Eden for the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.82,0:32:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.90,0:32:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.82,0:32:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉亚怂恿他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amelia was egging him on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.78,0:32:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她对大卫说  如果他爱她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She told David if he loved her,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.83,0:32:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就跳下去证明给她看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he'd prove it and jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.91,0:32:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-她推了他  -她用不着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- She pushed him? - She didn't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.96,0:32:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我弟弟一心只想着证明给她看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My brother was so obsessed with impressing her,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.67,0:32:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就决定跳下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he decided to dive.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.59,0:32:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个肩膀都撕裂了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ripped both his shoulders apart
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.46,0:32:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橄榄球前程也毁了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and ruined his football career,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.17,0:32:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都因为艾米莉亚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}all because of Amelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.38,0:32:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许他终于想报复了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe he's finally looking for payback.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.68,0:32:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.60,0:32:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉亚对男人有魔力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amelia has this power over men.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.97,0:32:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她对他们越差\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's like, the worse she treats them,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.06,0:32:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就越喜欢她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the more they like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.73,0:32:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾  她不见了  但是大卫不会绑架她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry she's missing, but David wouldn't take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.44,0:32:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是他自己出去找她了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's probably out looking for her himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.49,0:32:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right. Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.57,0:32:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你家湖边的房子后来怎样了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, whatever happened to your family house on the lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.16,0:32:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是我们的  怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We still own it. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.91,0:32:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是好奇  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just curious. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.14,0:33:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝新的开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}To fresh starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.73,0:33:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没钱怎么重新开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How do we start fresh without money?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.57,0:33:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.61,0:33:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经搞定了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I got this covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.41,0:33:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  过来看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, Mom, come and check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.37,0:33:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.95,0:33:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要给我看什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.33,0:33:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给动物们做了一个家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm making a house for the animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.91,0:33:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.96,0:33:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小篝火\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Little campfire?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.71,0:33:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So good.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.71,0:33:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Having fun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.13,0:33:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾茜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gracie.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.80,0:33:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈和我想告诉你一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's something your mother and I wanna tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.56,0:33:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别现在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.89,0:33:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带格蕾茜进去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take Gracie inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.35,0:33:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来处理这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.40,0:33:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放松  熊爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Relax, Papa Bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.40,0:33:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们开始新生活需要的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everything we need to start a new life
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.99,0:33:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在那辆车上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is in that car.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.75,0:34:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.25,0:34:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个老朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}An old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.00,0:34:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是他家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.07,0:34:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佛蒙特州伊甸草地巷49号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}49 Meadow Lane, Eden, Vermont.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.03,0:34:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}On our way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.16,0:34:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.33,0:34:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉亚为什么要回到事故地点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why would Amelia go back to the scene of the accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.66,0:34:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她这种心理变态类型\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Her brand of psychopathy
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.92,0:34:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要通过重塑才能活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}requires reinvention to survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.54,0:34:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而重塑需要切断所有过去的联系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and reinvention requires cutting all ties to the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.92,0:34:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到湖边的房子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Isn't going back to the lake house
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.38,0:34:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是背道而驰吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the opposite of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.67,0:34:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果她是回去洗清原罪就不算\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not if she's returning to cleanse her original sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.47,0:34:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先她处理了丈夫和继子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}First she took care of the husband and the stepson.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.05,0:34:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后是萨姆  但她不认识他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And Sam, but she didn't know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.64,0:34:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What about Peter?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.14,0:34:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取决于他还有没有用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mm, depends if he's still useful or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.56,0:34:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作恶者变成了受害者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The perpetrator becomes the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.02,0:34:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道大卫·柯林斯是不是也是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wonder if the same holds true for David Collins.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.73,0:35:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对艾米莉亚  一切皆有可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}With Amelia, anything's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.07,0:35:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照你说的  三本护照\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Three passports, as requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.37,0:35:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞机票呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Plane tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.41,0:35:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有引渡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No extradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.25,0:35:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你忘了什么东西吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Think you're forgetting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.12,0:35:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你的吗  不可能忘记\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For you? No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.80,0:35:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,树下箱子里的七万五千元\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}75K from the trunk under the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.38,0:35:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真难挖啊  顺便说一句\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Which was a pain to dig up, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.76,0:35:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎么知道存款的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How does he know about the nest egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.68,0:35:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们要去挖那口箱子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If we'd gone to dig up that trunk,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.22,0:35:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我俩现在已经穿着橙色囚衣了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we'd both be in orange jumpsuits by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.36,0:35:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我更喜欢绿色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I prefer green.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.82,0:35:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那份  一万元\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your cut. Ten grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.61,0:35:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说好的是两万\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Deal was 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.07,0:35:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事前一万  事后一万\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ten before, ten after.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.03,0:35:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么尾款\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}After what?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.12,0:35:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我渴了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.66,0:35:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  你带她去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Go on. Take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.21,0:35:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  格蕾茜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, Gracie.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.14,0:36:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备好了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You ready to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.18,0:36:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你希望我做的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you really want me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.35,0:36:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在计划之中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All part of the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.06,0:36:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们在去机场的路上顺路去银行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then we stop by the bank on the way to the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.44,0:36:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你进去拿到五十万\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You go in and pick up that 500 grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.11,0:36:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就变成通缉女匪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I'm a wanted woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.07,0:36:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, you are. Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.87,0:36:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈  你来看这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, Mom, come and check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.75,0:36:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  宝贝  我马上到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One minute, sweetie. I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.59,0:36:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去找格蕾茜  带她去安全的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Grab Gracie. Take her to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.80,0:36:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分两路把车包围起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Around the car on both sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.73,0:36:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-联调局  举起手来  -联调局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- FBI! Hands in the air! - FBI!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.27,0:37:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举起手来  站住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hands in the air! Stop right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.27,0:37:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-所有人不许动  -妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Nobody move! - Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.06,0:37:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动  别动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't move! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.94,0:37:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举起手来  站在原地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hands up! Stay right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.03,0:37:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动  不许动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't move! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.74,0:37:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大  看到两件武器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Boss, see two weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.45,0:37:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放艾米莉亚走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let Amelia go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.12,0:37:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想抓的是我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's me you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.12,0:37:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.87,0:37:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我看来  这可不像绑匪和人质\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}From where I stand, it doesn't look like a captor and his hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.12,0:37:20.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你似乎被骗了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Looks like a guy who's been played.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.63,0:37:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉亚并不爱你  彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amelia doesn't love you, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.17,0:37:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在骗你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.96,0:37:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别听他的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.13,0:37:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在说实话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.43,0:37:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位柯林斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Collins over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.97,0:37:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他才是为她牺牲了自己的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he's the one who sacrificed himself for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.14,0:37:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  大卫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right, David?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.72,0:37:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时她说  "你要是真的爱我  会跳的"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When she said, "If you really love me, you'll jump"?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.27,0:37:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当时让我杀萨姆之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's what you said to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.02,0:37:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是这么跟我说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}before you made me kill Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.44,0:37:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.90,0:37:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得  我永远不会背叛你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Peter, I would never betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.57,0:37:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的儿子和老公在自己家里被杀之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I bet your son and husband thought that
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.37,0:37:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定也是这么想的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}before they were shot dead in their own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.54,0:37:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么做  彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't do it, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.79,0:38:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不希望事情无法收场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You don't want this to end the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.42,0:38:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来猜猜  艾米莉亚  这里有三本护照\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let me guess, Amelia, you got three passports over there:
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.34,0:38:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个给你  一个给格蕾茜  一个给大卫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}one for you, one for Gracie, and one for David.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.96,0:38:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得从来不在你的最终计划里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Peter was never part of the end plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.01,0:38:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大卫坚持的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}David insisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.81,0:38:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我想让他帮忙  他必须跟着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If I wanted his help, he had to come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.52,0:38:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且要带上枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And to bring his gun
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.18,0:38:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你可以在离开之前处理掉彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so you could take care of Peter before you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.77,0:38:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你想要我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You said you wanted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.36,0:38:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么能这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How could you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.36,0:38:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾茜是我们的女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gracie's our daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.83,0:38:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你唯一需要的男人  是你父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The only man you ever really needed was your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.62,0:38:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他从来没有回应你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And he was never there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.58,0:38:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个人只是被你利用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You just used those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.75,0:38:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你本打算拿着钱  带着女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You were gonna take the money and your daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.79,0:38:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接逃走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.71,0:38:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.88,0:38:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双手放在背后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Put your hands behind your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.55,0:38:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手放在背后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hands behind your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.43,0:38:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放在背后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Behind your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.65,0:39:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-放下武器  -不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Drop the weapon! - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.65,0:39:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下武器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Drop the weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.12,0:39:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-放开我  -双手背后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Get off me! - Hands behind your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.59,0:39:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stop moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.59,0:39:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  你看我  看着我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gonna be okay. Look at me. Look at me. Look at me.
