Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.11,0:40:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克罗斯比\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Crosby.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.20,0:40:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肯定是落在店里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ah, must've left them at the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.41,0:40:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  我回去取吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's okay. I'll go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.24,0:40:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你会玩乐器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I heard you're a musician.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.20,0:40:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听说对了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You heard right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.12,0:40:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待哪天听听你的演奏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I'm looking forward to hearing you play sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.83,0:40:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈娜通常都会戴上耳机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hana usually puts in her headphones.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.30,0:40:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉我忘拿你的药了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am so sorry I left your pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.51,0:40:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.64,0:40:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.85,0:40:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我脑海中总是不停回放那时的画面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just keep replaying what happened over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.61,0:40:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈娜  你不能这样想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hana, you can't go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.73,0:40:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在上武器处理课的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We learn how to deal with this stuff all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.40,0:40:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学了很多次如何应对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in weapons retention class.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.24,0:40:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.28,0:40:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们怎么说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And what do they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.45,0:40:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们在被绑架之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}People sometimes go crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.83,0:40:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通常会很疯狂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when they're about to get arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.20,0:40:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你处理好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But you handled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.12,0:40:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的努力很可能阻止了老大中枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you probably prevented the boss from taking a bullet in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.33,0:41:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你不能再自责了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So you gotta stop beating yourself up
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.54,0:41:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我  我能做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and tell me what I can do to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.63,0:41:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你饿吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.42,0:41:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不必这样照顾我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You don't have to play nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.88,0:41:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我愿意  来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I want to. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.64,0:41:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我特别会做红肠煎蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I make a killer bologna omelet
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.35,0:41:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者加热千层面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or warm up lasagna.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.22,0:41:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有芝士脆片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cheese crisp?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.43,0:41:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的厨艺留给泽蒂吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Save your cooking prowess for Zadie.
