Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.52,0:41:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现实点吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's be real.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.02,0:41:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得三周不能下地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm gonna be off my feet for three weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.78,0:41:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有一份全职工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You've got a full-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.74,0:41:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泽蒂很好  但她不可靠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Zadie's great, but she's unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.82,0:41:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回达利安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm gonna go home to Darien,
