Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.20,0:41:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确定吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.66,0:41:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很确定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.00,0:41:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以跟泽蒂二人世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't act like you're not gonna enjoy
